{
  "id": "adv_card_rei_14_02",
  "title": "一ノ瀬怜",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ricefield-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "ricefield-00-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "sfx",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-out-single-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_14_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_14_02-rei001.m4a",
      "text": "お待たせしました\n撮影の準備はもう出来ていますか？",
      "startTime": 2.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ricefield-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "ricefield-00-noon",
      "startTime": 5.5666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_14_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_14_02-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "あぁ、怜。いつでも始められるそうだ\nそれは今回の衣装だよな。よく似合っているぞ",
      "startTime": 9.0958050812,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ricefield-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "ricefield-00-noon",
      "startTime": 13.9666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_14_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_14_02-rei002.m4a",
      "text": "ありがとうございます\nさっき、スタッフさん達にも褒めてもらえたんです",
      "startTime": 15.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ricefield-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "ricefield-00-noon",
      "startTime": 19.1666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_14_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_14_02-rei003.m4a",
      "text": "セーラーモチーフって、海のイメージがありましたけど\n意外と、こういう場所にも合いますね",
      "startTime": 23.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_14_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_14_02-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "あぁ。それにしても、今日は晴れてくれて良かったな\n日差しが強過ぎるのだけが、少し心配だが……",
      "startTime": 31.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ricefield-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "ricefield-00-noon",
      "startTime": 35.5
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_14_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_14_02-rei004.m4a",
      "text": "気温も高いですけど、カラッとした暑さなので\nこれぐらいなら全然問題ないです",
      "startTime": 39.5950296372,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ricefield-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "ricefield-00-noon",
      "startTime": 42
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_14_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_14_02-rei005.m4a",
      "text": "あ、スタッフさんが呼んでいるみたいです\n行ってきますね、{user}さん",
      "startTime": 45.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_14_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_14_02-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "いってらっしゃい\n俺もここから、怜の活躍を見守っているよ",
      "startTime": 48.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ricefield-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "ricefield-00-noon",
      "startTime": 51.9
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_14_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_14_02-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "（いつにも増して、いい笑顔になっているな）\n（地方の解放感でリラックス出来ているのかもしれない）",
      "startTime": 55.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――数時間後",
      "startTime": 60.2000002543,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_camera-01.m4a",
          "delay": 10499.999745700003,
          "startTime": 70.7
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ricefield-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "ricefield-00-noon",
      "startTime": 61.2000002543
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ricefield-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "ricefield-00-noon",
      "startTime": 69.3
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_14_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_14_02-rei006.m4a",
      "text": "もう少し可愛らしいポーズ、ですか？\n……こんな感じでどうでしょう？",
      "startTime": 69.3,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_camera-01.m4a",
          "delay": 2000.0035603000015,
          "startTime": 71.3000035603
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_camera-01.m4a",
          "delay": 6566.6666666,
          "startTime": 75.8666666666
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_camera-01.m4a",
          "delay": 6033.333333300007,
          "startTime": 75.3333333333
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ricefield-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "ricefield-00-noon",
      "startTime": 71.3000035603
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_14_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_14_02-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "（撮影は順調に進んでいるが……あれからだいぶ）\n（気温も日差しも強くなってきているな。……よし）",
      "startTime": 75.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ricefield-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "ricefield-00-noon",
      "startTime": 80.1000035603
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_14_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_14_02-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "すみません、この辺りで一度、休憩をいただいても\nよろしいでしょうか？　はい。ありがとうございます",
      "startTime": 83.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ricefield-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "ricefield-00-noon",
      "startTime": 87.666670227
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_14_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_14_02-rei007.m4a",
      "text": "どうしたんですか、{user}さん？\n撮影を止めたりなんかして",
      "startTime": 89.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_14_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_14_02-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "炎天下の中、ずっと日差しの下にいるだろう？\nだから一度、水分補給でもどうかと思ったんだ",
      "startTime": 95.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ricefield-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "ricefield-00-noon",
      "startTime": 99.1000035603
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_14_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_14_02-rei008.m4a",
      "text": "お気遣いありがとうございます\nでも、別にまだ大丈夫でしたよ？",
      "startTime": 101.4,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_gasa-02.m4a",
          "delay": 7466.666666699993,
          "startTime": 108.8666666667
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_14_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_14_02-rei009.m4a",
      "text": "確かに暑くなってきていますけど\n心配、し過ぎ……っ……",
      "startTime": 106.7037482262,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ricefield-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "ricefield-00-noon",
      "startTime": 108.8666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_14_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_14_02-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "怜！　どうした、少しフラついたか？\nそこの木陰に移動しよう",
      "startTime": 112.5333292644,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_drink-01.m4a",
          "delay": 10833.333333300005,
          "startTime": 123.3666625977
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_busstop-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "busstop-00-noon",
      "startTime": 115.5500010173
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_busstop-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "busstop-00-noon",
      "startTime": 115.5500010173
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_14_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_14_02-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "ほら、水を持ってきたからゆっくり飲むといい\n焦らず、ゆっくり飲むんだぞ",
      "startTime": 120.2773038783,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_busstop-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "busstop-00-noon",
      "startTime": 122.899995931
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_busstop-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "busstop-00-noon",
      "startTime": 125.1333318075
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_14_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_14_02-rei010.m4a",
      "text": "ありがとうございます、{user}さん\nなんだか、力が抜けて、ぼーっとしちゃって……",
      "startTime": 130.0333282472,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_busstop-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "busstop-00-noon",
      "startTime": 134.8999984742
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_14_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_14_02-rei011.m4a",
      "text": "こんなに暑いのに、汗も全然出ないみたいで\nでも、さっきまでは大丈夫だったのに……",
      "startTime": 138.9666615805,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_busstop-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "busstop-00-noon",
      "startTime": 142.2999984742
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_14_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_14_02-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "水を飲んでも汗をかかないなら\n熱中症になりかけているのかもしれないな",
      "startTime": 144.9666615805,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_14_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_14_02-rei012.m4a",
      "text": "っ……すみません。自分じゃ気付けなくて……\nもっと早めに水分補給しておくべきでした",
      "startTime": 155.0944990741,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_busstop-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "busstop-00-noon",
      "startTime": 158.3666651409
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_14_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_14_02-rei013.m4a",
      "text": "撮影を止めちゃいましたし、スタッフさん達にも\n迷惑を掛けて……プロとして情けないです",
      "startTime": 161.799995931,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_busstop-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "busstop-00-noon",
      "startTime": 166.6666651409
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_14_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_14_02-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "気にすることないさ。それに、まだ軽度のようだから\n木陰で休んでいればすぐに良くなるはずだ",
      "startTime": 170.9666615805,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_14_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_14_02-koh012.m4a",
      "text": "ハンディファンを借りてきたから\nとりあえずこれで体を冷やすといい",
      "startTime": 175.8666534425,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_busstop-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "busstop-00-noon",
      "startTime": 178.3666570028
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_14_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_14_02-rei014.m4a",
      "text": "ありがとうございます……。体調不良で倒れるなんて\nもうこんなことはしないって決めてたのに……",
      "startTime": 183.7333201092,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_busstop-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "busstop-00-noon",
      "startTime": 186.8999903362
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
